{"tid":1953563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯去信林鄭　建議「仿效日本」 九月立法會選舉延期","createTime":"2020-04-01T08:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T09:11:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"163431ffd47af668321f41869bf212939463d51c","tid":1953563,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，近日大力推動政府盡快就 23 條立法的建制派派議員何君堯，昨日去信行政長官林鄭月娥，建議延遲今年 9 月的立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯的信件指，武漢肺炎令多國受嚴重影響，日本政府亦不惜代價壓後一年才舉行東京奧運，他「極之支持」特首果斷加強規管群眾聚集，但近兩周從歐美回港的人數激增，令感染人數跳升，疫情走勢難以預料，建議為「安全和公平」起見，考慮「仿效日本」將九月立法會選舉延期。<br />\n<br />\n他表示希望林鄭月娥及早考慮和作出決定，以便社會能調整和作相應安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A8%B1%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%9B%A3%E6%96%99-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2596%2599-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E6%259C%259F%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmna0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=58a148af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2596%2599-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25BB%25B